full_text:
A great week supporting the use of our @EquineMediRec system for all the horses that raced in @TheSaudiCup 2024 Festival. Thank you to everyone who helped us to ensure equine welfare protocols were followed!

Photo credit: @deborahburt1 

#EquineWelfare #SaudiCup https://t.co/Lb2jF63pZQ

full_text:
#SaudiCup: 

White Abarrio is a deserved favorite here, but 6/5 is too much to stomach in 14-horse field with so many wild cards.

Loved National Treasure in Pegasus but spacing isn't quite right here to fire his best, can't use at 5-1.

Going to center most of my bets around Brad Cox and Saudi Crown at 16-1. PA Derby and Jim Dandy efforts definitely give him a shot and that's a great price.

Derma Sotogake has a chance for sure, 6-1 is probably close to proper price.  Drifting up to 8-1 now, might be worth a sniff. Isolate is another one with value at 32-1.  I'll probably use both.  Not without a possibility that Hoist The Gold could steal this on the front end.

#saudicup2024

It was amazing to deploy the Arabic version of our EMR system for @TheSaudiCup. Thank you to @JCSA_Racing for supporting us and all the trainers and veterinarians who made the launch of our system a success!

Photo credit: @DeborahBurt1 

#EquineWelfare #SaudiCup https://t.co/SxJEm050By
User Description: EMR develops, sells and maintains an award winning software platform to help horse trainers/owners comply with latest equine welfare regulations and protocols

text: #SaudiArabia has also hosted the 4th edition of the #SaudiCup, an international horse race held in #Riyadh. The Saudi Cup 2023 featured the participation of 243 horses from 16 countries. It is clear that #SaudiArabia continues to rise as a global hub for sports events.
